<P><HI>Holder (Chri&s;topher)</HI> and <HI>John Copeland,</HI> cruelly whipt, impri&s;on'd, and inhumanly u&s;ed at <HI>Bo&s;ton</HI> in <HI>New-England,</HI> 169. They with <HI>John Rous</HI> have their right Ears cut off, and are afterwards whipt in the Hou&s;e of Correction, 194.</P>
