<P><HI>Hooton (Elizabeth)</HI> one of the fir&s;t that came to be convinced of the inward Divine Teaching, 13. Is moved to preach publichly, 35. Others before her had preach'd in large Meetings at <HI>London,</HI> 36. She is cruelly u&s;ed in <HI>New-England,</HI> 326, 327.</P>
