<P>Law, either Outward or Inward; this la&s;t, <HI>viz.</HI> the Law of God in the Mind convinces of Sin, 15.</P>
<P>Laws de&s;igned originally again&s;t <HI>Papi&s;ts,</HI> execu|ted again&s;t Prote&s;tant Di&s;&s;enters, 255. An Ab|&s;tract of them, inter&s;pers'd with Ca&s;es, 256, 257.</P>
