<P><HI>Magna C<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">arta</HI> Proceedings again&s;t <HI>Quakers</HI> con|trary to it, 341.</P>
<P><HI>Malta, Engli&s;h</HI> Con&s;ul there, acce&s;&s;ary to the putting two <HI>Engli&s;h</HI> Women in the Inqui&s;ition, 286. His Death, 299. A dreadful Tempe&s;t and Earth|quake there, 304. <HI>K. Evans</HI> writes to their Rulers, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">03.</P>
