<P><HI>Mar&s;h<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"></HI> (&mdash;) <ABBR>E&s;q</ABBR> one of the King's Bed-cham|ber, a Friend to <HI>G. Fox,</HI> 253. His extraordinary Re&s;pect for him, 444. Is made Ju&s;tice of Peace, Continues kind to <HI>G. F.</HI> and other Friends, 559.</P>
